    • createCamp

      public Camp createCamp(Staff staff, String campName, TimeRegion region, LocalDate regCloseDate, String userGroup, String location, int totalSlots, int campCommitteeSlot, String description)
      creates a camp
      Parameters:
      staff - Staff object.
      campName - The name of this camp.
      region - The duration (start and end date) of this camp.
      regCloseDate - The registration deadline of this camp.
      userGroup - Which group(faculty) of students is this camp open to.
      location - Location where this camp will be held at.
      totalSlots - Number of total slots for this camp (Camp attendee + Camp committee slots).
      campCommitteeSlot - Number of camp committee slots for this camp.
      description - Description of this camp.
      Returns:
      Camp object that is created.

    • deleteCamp

      public void deleteCamp(Staff staff, Camp camp, UserController userController) throws CampControllerException
      Delete the camp object.
      Parameters:
      staff - Staff object that is using the CAM system to delete the camp.
      camp - Target Camp object that the Staff want to delete.
      userController - Controller class of the User class.
      Throws:
      CampControllerException - Display the reason why this camp cannot be deleted.
